[EV71 is one of several viruses that can cause HFMD. While the disease is usually mild, EV71 sometimes leads to neurological complications in young children. Because of this, EV71 has received increased attention as a cause of HFMD. This research has opened a door to find a means of preventing neurologic complications following infection with this virus. - Mod.LK]
